        "content": "<p>Hi</p>\n<p>First I'm sorry if it's duplicated question.<br>\nI'm very new for Zulip and failed to search the same topic.</p>\n<p>I'm trying to make some example drivers in the Linux Device Drivers book.<br>\nAnd I failed to handle String data when making proc driver.</p>\n<p>(Please understand that I'm attaching links of my code not to bother you with long dummy code.)</p>\n<p>Here it makes an array of static str.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/gurugio/rust-for-linux/blob/rust-next-ldd-ch05/samples/rust/rust_ldd05.rs#L24\">https://github.com/gurugio/rust-for-linux/blob/rust-next-ldd-ch05/samples/rust/rust_ldd05.rs#L24</a></p>\n<p>And here it makes the CString with the static str and returns the pointer.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/gurugio/rust-for-linux/blob/rust-next-ldd-ch05/samples/rust/rust_ldd05.rs#L78\">https://github.com/gurugio/rust-for-linux/blob/rust-next-ldd-ch05/samples/rust/rust_ldd05.rs#L78</a></p>\n<p>Finally it prints the string.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/gurugio/rust-for-linux/blob/rust-next-ldd-ch05/samples/rust/rust_ldd05.rs#L99\">https://github.com/gurugio/rust-for-linux/blob/rust-next-ldd-ch05/samples/rust/rust_ldd05.rs#L99</a></p>\n<p>The result is below.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">heavens</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"n\">J</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"o\">@/</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"n\">arth</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creat</span><span class=\"err\">��</span><span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"err\">�����</span><span class=\"n\">ky</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">3</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dry</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">land</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">all</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">plant</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">life</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bq</span><span class=\"err\">`�`�</span><span class=\"n\">e</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">small</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">4</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">all</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">stars</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"n\">J</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"o\">@/</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"n\">venly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bodies</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">all</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">life</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">that</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"n\">J</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"o\">@/</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">water</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">6</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">all</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creat</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"n\">J</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"o\">@/</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"err\">�</span><span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">live</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">on</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dry</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">land</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">7</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rests</span><span class=\"err\">��</span><span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"err\">�����</span><span class=\"n\">ky</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I thought the final string data printed by seq_printf has NULL because it uses the pointer from CString.<br>\nI guess the broken characters are caused by non-NULL bytes.<br>\nCould you please give me a hint how to create a NULL-terminated string in Rust?</p>",
