    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"546447\">Benno Lossin</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/What.20is.20the.20correct.20way.20to.20print.20a.20String.3F/near/397330666\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>There is the <code>c_str!</code> macro that automatically adds a <code>\\0</code> to the end of your strings.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Now it's working well as below.<br>\nThank you very much ;-)</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">heavens</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">earth</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sky</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">3</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dry</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">land</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">all</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">plant</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">life</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">both</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">large</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">small</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">4</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">all</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">stars</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">heavenly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bodies</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">all</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">life</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">that</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">lives</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">water</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">6</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creates</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">all</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">creatures</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">that</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">live</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">on</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dry</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">land</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Day</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">7</span>: <span class=\"nc\">God</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rests</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
